				Why does everlore employ level 15's to talk about Proon/sol b/lower guk/plane mobs... <BR>
<BR>
First of all, Proon hits low for his level, ive seen a level 40 hit for 150. it goes up really... most level 35's hit for 90's then at 37+ its 100.<BR>
for soloers:<BR>
<BR>
Necromancer: have him darknessed and feared constantly, keep pet's taunt off until the end of fight where he charges you. if not, pet will die quickly.<BR>
<BR>
Druid: Use your kiting methods =P snare, blast, dot<BR>
<BR>
Magician: tuff one... root in between blasts I guess.<BR>
<BR>
level 10 warrior: Run your ass to me and I will save you.<BR>
<BR>
                         Volmort Plaguebearer<BR>
